Seq1.CallerContent: Hello, I was wondering if I could make an appointment?

Seq2.CallerContent: Is either one more faster, I guess, telehealth?

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Okay, one moment. Let me check on the next available slot for you.

Seq5.ReceiverContent: May I take your date of birth?

Seq6.CallerContent: My last name is Ferguson. First name, Patrick.
Seq6.ReceiverContent: May I know your last name, please?

Seq7.CallerContent: Just to check up on my... I've had like a really stiff neck and a headache lately. And I've had... My father died of an aneurysm and I just want to make sure that I'm not going down the same route.
Seq7.ReceiverContent: Okay, so is this going to be a regular checkup?

Seq8.CallerContent: Sure. A second thing is, I think I might have a hiatal hernia.

Seq9.ReceiverContent: Okay, so just confirm, I have an appointment on 21st of December at 2 p.m. for a tele-visit.

Seq10.ReceiverContent: Is there anything else that I may assist you with?

Seq11.ReceiverContent: Thanks for calling Crofton Family Practice and you have a great day.
